; probe-fusion.form вЂ” many trusted probes, each sensing a different aspect; channels fuse into new modalities.
;
; THE ASK (Urs): use the BEST transcriber, not whisper-tiny вЂ” the Form classifiers can only learn as well as
; the ground truth they learn from. Use ALL the trusted audio probes вЂ” even a fast Fourier spectrum analyzer
; gives really good signal вЂ” each to learn a different aspect of sound. And let channels use channels: combine
; multiple channels live into a FUSION вЂ” a new interface, a new modality.
;
; THE SHAPE: two kinds of probe, one fusion.
;   BODY PROBES (Form DSP, read the wav in-kernel вЂ” "why Python" answered: the kernel reads the wav in ~8 ms):
;     - wav-sense.fk (в†’63)   energy envelope, 8 windows 0..9.
;     - spectrum.fk (в†’15)    the FFT: a Goertzel filterbank, 8 bands 100..7000 Hz. The kernel has no sin/cos,
;                            so the band cosine coefficients are DATA and the recurrence is pure mul/add/sub;
;                            a real DFT-band spectrum, Form-native, float deterministic three-way.
;     - f0 (pitch)           autocorrelation вЂ” still in the carrier; the next DSP to lift the same way.
;   CARRIER ORACLES (best-quality host probes the body learns FROM вЂ” not the body, the ground truth):
;     - whisper-large-v3-turbo, kept RESIDENT (whisper_server.py: load once ~5 s, then ~0.5 s/chunk) вЂ” the
;       best transcriber, because the learner is bounded by its oracle. tiny was a bootstrap; large is the floor.
;     - SoundAnalysis (the swift sound-category oracle). ShazamKit / a VAD / diarization join the same way.
;   FUSION (field-fusion.fk): ff-fuse concatenates probe channels into ONE vector вЂ” a new modality. The
;     co-learning arm now learns on energy вЉ• spectrum (16 dims), which recognizes more than either alone;
;     spectrum вЉ• pitch вЉ• prosody becomes a timbre channel; a fused channel is itself a channel others fuse.
;
;   wav в”Ђв–є [ energy ]  [ spectrum ]  [ pitch ] в”Ђв”Ђв–є ff-fuse в”Ђв–є fused feature в”Ђв–є nearest-shape learns
;          (body DSP, in-kernel)                   (a new modality)            (from the best oracles)
;     в””в”Ђв–є [ whisper-large ] [ SoundAnalysis ] в”Ђв”Ђв–є the ORACLES the body learns from (champion в†’ challenger)
;
; в”Ђв”Ђ EXISTS (proven + wired live) в”Ђв”Ђ
;   spectrum.fk (в†’15, three-way) вЂ” the FFT filterbank, verified live (в–„в–€в–†в–‡в–Ѓв–ѓв–‚в–‚ over 100в†’7 kHz). wav-sense.fk
;   (в†’63) вЂ” energy. field-fusion.fk вЂ” ff-fuse. co-learning.fk / nearest-shape.fk вЂ” the learner. whisper_server.py
;   вЂ” the resident best oracle. All wired into channel_live.py: the fused energyвЉ•spectrum feature drives the
;   co-learning arm; a `spectrum` view (key f) shows the live bands; the oracle is large-v3-turbo by default.
;
; в”Ђв”Ђ THE RUNGS в”Ђв”Ђ
;   M0  best oracle + the FFT probe + fusion вЂ” SHIPPED + VERIFIED (this commit).
;   M1  lift f0 into Form (read the wav, autocorrelate in-kernel) вЂ” the last carrier DSP becomes body.
;   M2  more probes, same frame: ShazamKit (song id), a VAD, diarization (speaker id) вЂ” each a trusted
;       oracle or a body DSP; each learns a different aspect; each fuses.
;   M3  fused channels as first-class channels: a timbre channel (spectrumвЉ•pitch), a prosody channel
;       (energyвЉ•pitchвЉ•spectrum over time) вЂ” published on the broadcast, subscribable, themselves fusable.
;   M4  champion в†’ challenger per probe: once the Form-native arm on the fused feature reaches an oracle,
;       retire the expensive oracle for that category (colearning-retire.fk) вЂ” the circle hears on its own.
;
; KIN: live-transcribe-channel.form (the channel these probes feed) В· co-learning.form (learn from the best
;   oracle) В· field-fusion (the fusion body) В· spectrum.fk + wav-sense.fk (the body DSP probes) В·
;   recognition-router.form (fuse readings into one stream) В· champion-challenger.form (retire a reached oracle).
